title: Trayvon Bromell on 100m, positive mindset, and his journey to Tokyo 2020
description: The Olympic 100m final is one of the most iconic events on the entire planet. Trayvon Bromell set an early world leading time of 9.88 in May 2021. His whole life he has beaten the odds to become one of the favourites for Olympic glory in Tokyo.
